text.tspan: In all this fuss we clean forgot
Who dares stand between a mother and her daughter's life? Precia will do
anything to achieve her goals. Even if it means accepting Fate.

advanced hesitantly along the corridor, throwing a longing glance at the
sandy-haired woman alongside her. Long blonde hair swished softly at the
movement, and Linith looked down at her. The familiar's face was grave - a
startling contrast to the warm, kind demeanour she usually displayed. A hint of
